channel.title: Strange sram overflow outcome
channel.description: So i have this patch with 16 wave/play objects that when going live returns an sram overflow by 68 bytes. Just a patch to check how mutch sram an object uses. Now i made a mix object that just has 6 inputs , no bus or gain. I added it to the overflow patch to see how many sram i save compared to the normal mix 6 object and when i go live i end up with an overflow of 60 bytes. That is 8 less by adding an object. How is this possible?
